commit.message:
Capture a final set of updates to README.md that were somehow missed last
year.
Various minor tweaks and collateral damage from autotools and configuration.

A bunch of changes to get the examples working. Moved dylp's mps reader back
into the main code base. Finally figured out why dylp's bnfrdr parser failed
on windows; fixed in dylib_io.c and various places where it's used. Changes
for proper symbol export.
Remove the .ci directory; no longer used.

Pass the correct original row bounds vectors to postsolve. Plug a small
memory leak. Use context (cx*) options in unitTest. Various drive-by tweaks.

Changes to autotools sources, plus collateral damage. Upgrade tests
for isfinite, isnan to resolve issues with Apple M1. Add DylpTest and
OsiDylpTest units to get proper build flags for unit tests.
Collateral damage from change to DYLP_FIND_ISFINITE and DYLP_FIND_ISNAN macros.

Add __builtin_isfinite and __builtin_isnan to the list of names checked by
DYLP_FIND_ISFINITE and DYLP_FIND_ISNAN, respectively.

Tweak dylib_bnfrdr.c (add include for stdio.h) to try and cure a linking
problem with MS cl.
Turn off fail fast for windows CI to get more information.

Take another stab at getting configure.ac macros that'll find isfinite and
isnan on an Apple M1 system.

Clean up the old malloc trace macros so they're useable, should anyone ever
want to use them.

Remove a couple of variable length array declarations. Microsoft chooses not
to support this construct.
Add windows builds to the workflow.

A pile of changes to support symbol visibility hidden by default. Took the
opportunity to add honest dy_ prefixes to errmsg and warn. These changes will
almost certainly break code using dylp directly. Might be ok from OsiDylp.

First cut at getting CI going. Add the .github/workflows directory, with
linux-ci.yml.
A few more tweaks to config.yml. Temporarily redirect to my CoinUtils fork.
Forgot a Version line.
First stab at updating dependency info. Add config.yml.
Collateral damage from run_autotools.

Convert dy_errmsgs.txt into a const array of character strings in
dylib_errmsgs.c.  Relatively extensive rewrite for dylib_errs.c, collateral
damage for the rest.
Various trivial drive-by changes; white space, typos.
One line change to supply postsolve with row bounds from original system.
Collateral damage from updates to primary autotools files.

Changes to configure.ac, multiple Makefile.am, dylp.pc.in to finish bringing
dylp's autotools files into the modern world.

Tweak configure.ac to try a little harder to get an absolute path to
dy_errmsg.txt.

Copy the define of DYLP_ERRMSGDIR into config_dylp.h.in so it's available
outside of the library build. Temporary measure 'til I fix this properly.
New autotools helpers, not previously needed.
Update name of CoinTypes.h. Fix handling of ODSI_PARANOIA.
Collateral damage from BuildTools updates.
